      <h2 id="repo">The repo</h2>

      <p>The Umami Post is a complete, production-grade static publication built on Eleventy. The whole codebase -- every layout, every partial, every line of CSS, every utility filter -- is in the repository. No private dependencies, no closed-source plugin, nothing waiting for a license fee.</p>

